c: 22
v: 26
t: "Ndi pamene tidamulangiza Abrahamu malo omangapo Mzikiti Woyera tidamuuza kuti, “Usapembedze wina aliyense koma Ine ndekha. Ndipo yeretsa nyumba yanga kuti izikhala yaukhondo chifukwa cha anthu amene amayenda kuizungulira iyo ndi iwo amene amaimirira kapena amagwada ndi kuwerama popembedza.”"